    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0776b09"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000010769">揚州慧照寺</placeName><persName key="A010515">崇演</persName>傳</head><p>
<lb ed="T" n="0776b10"/><persName key="A010515">釋崇演</persName>，姓段氏，<placeName key="PL000000021676">東平</placeName>人也。出家于本州<placeName key="PL000000021655">龍興
<lb ed="T" n="0776b11"/>寺</placeName><persName key="A002130">慧超法師</persName>之門。遊方問道，見<placeName key="PL000000023260">嵩陽</placeName><persName key="A010517">善寂禪
<lb ed="T" n="0776b12"/>師</persName>，示其心法。後居<placeName key="PL000000010610">都梁山</placeName>，當于<placeName key="PL000000010590">淮浦</placeName>，四面
        <lb ed="T" n="0776b13"/>來商毳客影附焉。相國<persName key="A010516">李公紳</persName>鎮撫<placeName key="PL000000010783">廣陵</placeName><note resp="sgsz">案《舊唐書．卷173．<persName key="A010516">李紳</persName>傳》：「（<date key="j20255132025541" to-iso="0833-08-22" from-iso="0833-07-25">大和七年七月</date>），檢校左常侍、<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName>刺史、<placeName key="PL000000011308">浙東</placeName>觀察使。……<ref type="date" target="#j20279082028259">武宗即位</ref>，加檢校尚書右僕射、揚州大都督府長史，知淮南節度大使事。<date key="j20282682028642" from-iso="0841-02-08" to-iso="0842-02-17">會昌元年</date>，入為兵部侍郎。……<date key="j20296762029705" to-iso="0845-01-15" from-iso="0844-12-17">（會昌四年）十一月</date>，守僕射、平章事，出為<placeName key="PL000000010783">淮南</placeName>節度使。<date key="j20300902030170" from-iso="0846-02-04" to-iso="0846-04-25">六年</date>，卒。」當<persName key="A010516">李紳</persName>鎮撫<placeName key="PL000000010783">廣陵</placeName>，<persName key="A010515">崇演</persName>已圓寂七年矣！</note>，而
<lb ed="T" n="0776b14"/>性剛嚴，少所接與，偏輕釋子。或允相見，必
<lb ed="T" n="0776b15"/>問難鋒起，祇應不供者，多咄叱而出。<persName key="A010516">紳</persName>遣衙
        <lb ed="T" n="0776b16"/>吏<persName key="A019234">章幼成</persName>傳意召<persName key="A010515">演</persName>入府，詶對詣理，談論
<lb ed="T" n="0776b17"/>鏗然。<persName key="A010516">紳</persName>惘然，翻不測其畛域，特加歸信，請
<lb ed="T" n="0776b18"/>居<placeName key="PL000000010769">慧照寺</placeName>化導。同聲相應，僅于千眾。<date from-iso="0837-02-13" key="j20268122027166" to-iso="0838-02-02">開成
    <lb ed="T" n="0776b19"/>二年</date>，終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010769">淨院</ref>，春秋八十四。以<date key="j20271002027100" when-iso="0837-11-28">十月二十三
<lb ed="T" n="0776b20"/>日</date>全身入塔云。</p>
